tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE robot_logs (
    log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id UUID NOT NULL,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    log_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE diagnostics (
  diagnostic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  robot_id INT,
  battery_voltage DECIMAL(5,2),
  cpu_temperature DECIMAL(5,2),
  diagnostic_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE error_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id INT,
    error_message TEXT,
    error_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    error_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE diagnostics (
    diagnostic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id INT,
    diagnostic_message TEXT,
    diagnostic_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE robots (
    robot_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_name VARCHAR(50),
    manufacturing_date DATE,
    firmware_version VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE maintenance_logs (
    maintenance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id INT,
    maintenance_message TEXT,
    maintenance_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE error_logs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_message TEXT,
    error_code INT,
    robot_id INT,
    error_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE system_diagnostics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_id INT,
    diagnostic_message TEXT,
    diagnostic_code INT,
    robot_id INT,
    diagnostic_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE robots (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_name VARCHAR(50),
    operational_status VARCHAR(20),
    creation_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE log_types (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    type_name VARCHAR(30),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE robot_statistics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id INT,
    total_errors INT,
    total_diagnostics INT,
    last_activity TIMESTAMP
)
